svg.text: CONCLUSION: P ≠ NP as Physical Necessity
Five independent foundations converge on a single structural constraint:
"The asymmetry between construction and verification is not a bug in our algorithms—it is a feature of operational space itself."

g.text: In any composable system with non-invertibility,
